Looks like i was able to build the tensorflow 1.7.0 but when I try to import it into python3.6 i get the same error as above

    return load_dynamic(name, filename, file)
  File "/usr/lib/python3.6/imp.py", line 343, in load_dynamic
    return _load(spec)
